videos.description: Bruins RB Bolu Olorunfunmi pushes the pile for a 1-yard TD run, giving UCLA an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: UCLA strikes first with goal-line TD

videos.headline: Cincinnati WR makes diving catch to set up TD

videos.description: Bearcats safety James Wiggins picks it off the turf to intercept UCLA and set up the Bearcats' go-ahead TD.
videos.headline: Speight gets picked off

videos.description: Bruins RB Kazmeir Allen outruns the Bearcats defense for a game-tying touchdown early in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: UCLA rips off 74-yd TD run

videos.description: UCLA backup QB Dorian Thomas-Robinson is stripped. The Bruins recover in the end zone, giving the Bearcats a go-ahead safety.
videos.headline: Cincinnati defense creates fumble and safety

videos.description: Bearcats RB Michael Warren II punches it in from a yard out to make it 26-17 Cincinnati in the closing minutes.
videos.headline: Cincinnati converts on 4th down for late TD
